//! TTS-ElevenLabs WASM Component
//!
//! Implements the golem:tts@1.0.0 WIT interface for ElevenLabs text-to-speech provider.
//!
//! ## Standard Compliance
//! - C1 (Totality): All functions have explicit returns.
//! - C2 (Explicitness): Explicit imports, no star imports, no unwrap().
//! - C3 (Determinism): External API calls wrapped in atomic operations.
//! - C4 (Local Reasoning): Explicit control flow, clear data ownership.
//! - C5 (Failure as Value): Comprehensive TtsError mapping.

